{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was somebody in charge who had to go and-- and haul it into each camp to distribute for the people to eat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were looking, one day, for a guy who would-- who would be-- take this over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody wanted the job, because everybody wanted to eat from the food that was in the camp that-- that came-- rather that came with the people, which was much better stuff, whichever-- whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So and I was kind of hurt by the guy what he-- that he beat me up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went to the guy who was in charge, whatever, and I volunteered for this job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And since my name was Mittelman, and the food that we have to draw was [GERMAN] called in German, so they called me the [GERMAN], which takes a half a word from my name and puts it in the word there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I was assigned a special two rooms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of them in which I can sleep by myself rather than with the rest of the guys in the bunk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And another room, which was like kind of a place where I keep all the stuff that I'm bringing in, the bread and so forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, since this was a time were nobody was eating the food that people drew from the main canteen-- And I used to come in the morning, let's say I had-- I don't remember how many people were there, maybe 300, 400.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I would bring in, maybe, for 300, 400 people, 150 breads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we'd-- we'd cut them in quarters, and some margarine and some-- and some whatever that came with it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to go-- and then the coffee or soup or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
